<div class="faq" id="FAQ">
    <div class="faq-title">
        <h1>FAQs</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="questions">
         
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">What is Meal Maker?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Meal Maker is a smart recipe generator that helps you turn your available ingredients into delicious recipes. Whether you're selecting ingredients from our list or typing in your own, Meal Maker instantly finds recipes you can cook without the stress of planning. It’s perfect for reducing food waste, saving time, and making cooking fun—even when your fridge looks empty!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">How does the recipe generator work?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Our recipe generator creates meal ideas based on the ingredients you select. Just pick what you have in your kitchen, and we’ll show you recipes you can make with them!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">What if an ingredient I have isn't listed?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                No problem! You can manually type in any missing ingredient, and our generator will include it when suggesting recipes.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">Do I need to select all ingredients I have?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Not necessarily. Just choose the key ingredients you want to use. The generator will find recipes that match as closely as possible.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">Can I save or download a recipe I like?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Yes! Once you've generated a recipe, you’ll find an option to export it as a PDF. This makes it easy to print, save for later, or share with others offline.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">Are the recipes vegetarian/vegan/gluten-free friendly?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Absolutely! You can filter recipes by dietary preferences after generating them or even before by applying filters on the ingredients page.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">Can I generate a recipe using only one ingredient?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Yes, even with a single ingredient, we’ll suggest simple recipes or pair it with commonly available ingredients to create something delicious!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-question" id="faqToggle">Can I choose a specific cuisine or meal type?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer">
                Yes! Meal Maker lets you filter recipes by cuisine (like Italian, Indian, or Chinese) and meal type (like breakfast, lunch, dinner, or snacks) so you get results that match your mood and preferences.
            </div>
        </div>


    </div>
</div>